Error:
   During the Compliation phase,before the program can even run.this called in Syntax error.the compiler cannot understand.
   Example : 
    missing semicolons,incorrect method signature,mismatch data type,unhandle checked exception.

Exception :
    Runtime Exeuation of a program.unexception or expectional events that disrupt the normal flow of the program.
